        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Preventing Foreclosures on Seniors Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill expands loss mitigation for borrowers and surviving spouses under the Federal Housing Administration's&nbsp;Home Equity Conversion Mortgages program (a reverse-mortgage program) and otherwise revises the program.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
